title: This app is the greatest source of information.
text: This app saves so much time searching for specific things. It gives me so many responses to my questions that I could never get from Google or any other kind of information requesting App. It helped me find more selections of movies on Netflix in the categories that I asked for, specifically, nonviolent, interesting, subject, and uplifting. It came up with so many selections that I could never find on Netflix in their search category. I also asked them to give me a list of hashtags for my Facebook page for pet portraits, and it gave me wonderful hashtags that I could never think of. This is my go to app to find out everything I need to know in less than a minute.
